127
00:10:15,840 --> 00:10:16,560
or dead.

128
00:10:19,000 --> 00:10:20,640
Only alive.

129
00:10:21,200 --> 00:10:22,000
Yes.

130
00:10:55,040 --> 00:10:56,280
Sorry, Miss.

131
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:59,120
You got injured in your face too bad

132
00:10:59,760 --> 00:11:00,720
