135
00:11:11,120 --> 00:11:12,040
You are...

136
00:11:12,480 --> 00:11:14,480
My name is Lin Cangwu.

137
00:11:15,240 --> 00:11:16,880
You saved me?

138
00:11:19,680 --> 00:11:21,400
I'll surely repay you

139
00:11:23,600 --> 00:11:24,880
