140
00:11:26,440 --> 00:11:27,920
May I have your name?

141
00:11:46,440 --> 00:11:47,600
My name is...

142
00:12:00,240 --> 00:12:01,040
Qin...

143
00:12:05,700 --> 00:12:06,600
Ruoyao.

144
00:12:07,720 --> 00:12:09,840
I'll haunt you down
even to the ends of the earth

145
00:12:11,240 --> 00:12:13,160
to find you.

